quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  105,1,Have you considered how your Lord dealt with the people of the Elephant
  105,2,Did He not bring their evil scheme to nothing
  105,3,He sent down upon them flocks of birds (unknown in the land)
  105,4,Shooting them with bullet-like stones of baked clay (an emblem of the punishment due to them)
  105,5,And so He rendered them like a field of grain devoured and trampled